OL,3,CPrince and Princess of Wales share
OL,4,Choliday photo to mark 15th anniversary
OL,6,FThe Prince and Princess of Wales have
OL,7,Fshared a holiday snapshot of their
OL,8,Ffamily, lying together in the grass in
OL,9,Fthe sunshine, to celebrate their 15th
OL,10,Fwedding anniversary.
OL,12,FIn the image taken by photographer
OL,13,FMatt Porteous, William and Kate are
OL,14,Fpictured with Prince George, Princess
OL,15,FCharlotte and Prince Louis, relaxing
OL,16,Fbarefoot during the Easter break.
OL,18,FLouis has his legs resting on Kate as
OL,19,Fthe family of five lie shoulder-to-
OL,20,Fshoulder on their backs in a row.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
