OL,3,CPrince and Princess of Wales share
OL,4,Choliday photo to mark 15th anniversary
OL,6,FTheir black cocker spaniel Orla makes
OL,7,Fan appearance next to William, as does
OL,8,Ftheir second dog ` a brown spaniel
OL,9,Fwhose name is yet to be revealed and
OL,10,Fwhich William and Kate kept from a
OL,11,Flitter of Orla's puppies.
OL,13,FWilliam was pictured with the puppies,
OL,14,Fand gazing at one of the brown ones,
OL,15,Fin a post to mark his birthday last
OL,16,Fyear.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
