OL,3,CPrince and Princess of Wales share
OL,4,Choliday photo to mark 15th anniversary
OL,6,FWednesday's wedding anniversary post
OL,7,Fon Kensington Palace's social media
OL,8,Fread: "Celebrating 15 years of
OL,9,Fmarriage" followed by a red heart
OL,10,Femoji.
OL,12,FThe photograph, capturing William and
OL,13,FKate's happy moment with their
OL,14,Fyoungsters, comes after the prince and
OL,15,Fprincess faced challenging times when
OL,16,FKate was diagnosed with cancer in 2024.
