OL,3,CPrince and Princess of Wales share
OL,4,Choliday photo to mark 15th anniversary
OL,6,FShe revealed last year she was in
OL,7,Fremission, and the Waleses made a
OL,8,Ffresh start by moving to a new home,
OL,9,Fthe eight-bedroom Forest Lodge in
OL,10,FWindsor Great Park, in the autumn.
OL,12,FThe couple, who met at St Andrews
OL,13,FUniversity, wed in a grand fairytale
OL,14,Fceremony in Westminster Abbey on April
OL,15,F29 2011, and kissed on the balcony of
OL,16,FBuckingham Palace afterwards.
OL,18,FWilliam and Kate welcomed their first
OL,19,Fchild George in 2013, followed by
OL,20,FCharlotte in 2015 and Louis in 2018.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
